        "timestamp": "2018-09-11 12:58:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Jim, did you have the chance to run either of the use cases in a\n > local installation to verify things ok?   And perhaps with\n > session-persistence apis?\n\nAmsterdam rules were verified with vCPE and casablanca with vCPE, vDNS, vFW, and VoLTE.  Regarding session-persistence, however, unfortunately, that cannot be verified at this time.  A bug was introduced when code was updated to store abatements; POLICY-1106 has been opened for this.",
